海、西安、长沙、深圳、杭州、昆明。 值得一提的是，山东有望成为今年「五一」旅游市场的新晋「顶流」。美团数据显示，该平台上住宿预订最热门的前二十个城市中，青岛、威海、济南、烟台等山东城市占了四席，淄博「五一」住宿预订量较 2019 年同期上涨了 800%。「五一」国内旅游订单创五年新高 部分目的地住宿预订量较 2019 年增长 1500%"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6b4dc00b6e51837c295320dd0eda5d5a_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "10 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/595017184"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IwcKEnIut8o1zEAMaCDk0NTA3MTcyIOm21aEGMAg4oAFALnIJNTk1MDE3MTg0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1681346298.6402175", "card_id": "Q_593079466", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何让小猫知道它自己叫什么名字？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "家里猫下小宝宝了，而且是七胞胎，该如何让每只猫知道自己叫啥啊，别到时候叫一声小黑，然后八只猫都跑过来了"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-5d5242bc784835b89c26078249a21664_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "10 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593079466"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IwcKEnIut8o1zEAMaCDk0MDc3MDkyIJThm6EGMAA4W0Avcgk1OTMwNzk0NjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1681346298.640855", "card_id": "Q_595238930", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 4 月 12 日正式发布的 RTX 4070 显卡，有哪些亮点？是否值得入手？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "10 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/595238930"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IwcKEnIut8o1zEAMaCDk0NTU2NTI3IJ/02qEGMAA4IEAwcgk1OTUyMzg5MzB4